":"September 13, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Zayd reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAmong the worst acts of usury is to disparage the reputation of a Muslim without right. Verily, this womb derives its name from the Most Merciful. Whoever severs its family ties, Allah will forbid him from entering\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38092,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/08\/11\/riba-decreases-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":11993,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Usury increases wealth, decreases rewards in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo one increases his wealth by usury except that his result will be little.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 2279 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u062d\u064e\u062f\u064c \u0623\u064e\u0643\u0652\u062b\u064e\u0631\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{